<p class="">Can I help the right hon. Gentleman? It probably means that the Assistance Board will be able to help those people who incur expenses subsequent to advice and treatment being given by a dentist outside the Assistance Board.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
