<p class="">Perhaps my hon. Friend, who always disagrees with all his medical colleagues over everything—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-262f61cc-b0ae-4336-b0e9-7f7cd05ab34e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
